Phil Jackson , a former National 
Basketball League coach, says Carmelo Anthony of the New York 
Knicks would benefit from reading his book, "Sacred Hoops." 
Jackson talks with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox, Carol Massar and Scott 
Soshnick on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:08
 